<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>뉴스룸 클론</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
</head>
<body>

<!-- 헤더 -->
<header class="header">
  <div class="logo">우아한형제들</div>
  <nav>
    <ul class="nav">
      <li>회사소개</li>
      <li>서비스</li>
      <li>지속가능경영</li>
      <li class="active">뉴스룸</li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- 메인 -->
<main>

  <!-- 상단 영역 -->
  <section class="top-area">
    <h1>뉴스룸</h1>

    <div class="search-box">
      <input type="text" placeholder="검색해보세요">
      <span>🔍</span>
    </div>

    <ul class="tabs">
      <li class="active">알립니다</li>
      <li>언론보도</li>
      <li>이슈와 팩트</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- 리스트 -->
  <section class="news-list">

    <!-- 아이템 1 -->
    <article class="news-item">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="">
      <div class="text">
        <h2>배민, 소규모 카페에 ‘BTS THE CITY SEOUL 음료’ 무상 지원한다</h2>
        <p class="date">2026.03.20</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 아이템 2 -->
    <article class="news-item">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="">
      <div class="text">
        <h2>우아한형제들, 데이터 기반 외식 트렌드 발표</h2>
        <p class="date">2026.03.18</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 아이템 3 -->
    <article class="news-item">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="">
      <div class="text">
        <h2>배달 플랫폼 시장 변화 리포트 공개</h2>
        <p class="date">2026.03.15</p>
      </div>
    </article>

  </section>

</main>

<!-- 푸터 -->
<footer class="footer">
  <p>© 우아한형제들</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>


